Upscale Beach Front Restaurant and Rooftop Lounge
1912 Ocean Bar & Rooftop offers spectacular views of the Atlantic, featuring indoor/outdoor seating and occupying the second and third floors of an all-new venue at Sawgrass Marriott's Cabana Beach Club. The menu features fresh seafood, small plates, elevated cocktails, and wines.
Join Marriott Bonvoy Today.
